hcc_text: Metropolitan Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top 10% for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Queens)
info: At Metropolitan Avenue at Union Turnpike, J Robinson Parkway Wb En Metropolit and 75th Road, there were 13 deaths and severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
